{{Otheruses|Seeker}}
The '''Seeker Transport''', also known as the '''message droid hyperspace pod''' was designed by [[Arakyd Industries/Legends|Arakyd Industries]] to provide their [[Seeker AS-M12 message droid|Seeker AS-M12]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]] with the capacity to travel between [[Star system/Legends|star systems]]. The design was based on their [[Viper probe droid/Legends|Viper probe droid]] [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] [[Hyperdrive pod/Legends|pod]], but modified for civilian purposes. Classed as a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]], the droid was 2 [[Meter/Legends|meters]] long, and was fully automated, although only capable of storing one jump in its [[Navigation computer/Legends|nav computer]]. It was capable of speeds up to 950 [[Kilometer/Legends|km]]/[[Standard hour/Legends|h]] in [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]].

Units typically cost 20,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]].

